snippet.title: JOHNNY DEPP AND HIS WIFE AMBER HEARD
snippet.description:
I started making this vídeo two months ago but I had a problem with my notebook... Anyway, here it is now!

Johnny and Amber got married in their house in Los Angeles first, in Feb 3rd, but a fewdays after that, on the weekend, they had a cerimony in his private island, in the Bahamas.

I chose this song because I knoe that both of them love country music and I really believe they found themselves in each other, somehow.
